Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=Deviation
  - 285
By: St Ignatius of Antioch
---
The Docetists abstain from the Eucharist, because they allow not that
It is the flesh of our Saviour, which flesh suffered for our sins, and
which the Father of His goodness raised up.
